[2026-07-15] [Ask My Docs / Observability] — Finding, not fixed: ObservabilityConfig.price_table ships with placeholder pricing ($3/$15 per Mtok sonnet, $1/$5 per Mtok haiku) per Decision 5 (verify against Anthropic's real published pricing before trusting cost numbers) — not corrected this build session, logged to BUGS.md.
